{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_05_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 真夏の障害物競走",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏フェス当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of Summer Festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ衣装に着替えたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about changing into your outfit soon?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、出番までまだ時間がありますから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ there's still time until my appearance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか本番ギリギリまで衣装を着ないつもりか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't tell me you plan to change into the outfit right before the performance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことはありません\nちゃんと着替えるので心配しないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's not the case.\nI will definitely change‚ so please don't worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だがリハでは、ダンスにいつものキレがなかったぞ\n本当は衣装が気になってるんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But during the rehearsal‚ your usual sharpness in the dance was missing.\nAre you really not concerned about the outfit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それは……確かに、新しい衣装のことを考えていて\n集中出来なかったことは認めます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I admit that I was thinking about the new outfit‚\nand it affected my concentration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなに衣装が気になるんだ？\nひょっとして、また……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you so concerned about the outfit?\nCould it be…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "またって、なんのことですか？　はっ、もしかして私が\nカロリー計算に失敗した時のことを思い出して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be… What are you referring to? Huh?\nCould it be because you're reminded of the time when I failed the calorie calculation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4040344238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……最低ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… {user}‚ that's awful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、今のは失言だった\nだから冷たい目で見ないでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ that was thoughtless of me.\nPlease don't give me such a cold look.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "体型はちゃんと維持してます\n毎日カロリー計算して太らないようにしてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I maintain my figure properly.\nI calculate my calories every day to prevent gaining weight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "計算に失敗しないように気をつけろよ……\nでも、ならどうしてそんなに着替えを嫌がるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Make sure not to make any mistakes in your calculations…\nBut then‚ why do you dislike changing so much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\nどうしても言わなくちゃダメですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well…\nDo I really have to tell you why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "心配なんだ。頼む、教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm worried. Please‚ tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないですね……\n実は、肌を露出した姿を見られるのが恥ずかしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine‚ I guess there's no helping it…\nActually‚ I feel embarrassed when someone sees me in a revealing outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "グラビアのお仕事もやってきたので\n見られることには慣れてるつもりだったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I've done gravure work before\nand thought I was used to being seen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "この間の試着の時、{user}さんに\n水着姿を見られるのが恥ずかしくなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But during the recent outfit fitting‚ when I try to let {user} look at me in a swimsuit‚\nI felt so embarrassed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4123255685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それ以来、人目が気になるようになってしまって\n自分でも困ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since then‚ I've become more conscious of being seen by others‚\nand I'm troubled by it myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルとはいえ年頃の女の子だ）\n（人目を意識して恥ずかしくなるのも無理ないか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's still a young girl‚ despite being an idol…）\n（It's not surprising for her to feel self-conscious and embarrassed in front of others…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "今日の夏フェスは特に観客が多いですし\n最近はサニピにも凄く注目が集まってるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's summer festival has a particularly large audience‚\nand there's been a lot of attention on Sunny Peace lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "大勢の人が私の水着姿を目に焼き付けるんだと思ったら\n緊張して体がこわばってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think that a large crowd of people will see me in a swimsuit‚\nI get nervous and my body stiffens…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "このままじゃいけないのは自分でも分かってます\nでも意識すればするほど恥ずかしさが増して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know I can't continue like this‚\nbut the more I'm aware of it‚ the more embarrassed I become…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（困ったな、何か意識を変えるきっかけを作れると）\n（いいんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is troublesome. I need to create a trigger to change her mindset…）\n（But what should I do…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
