      "text": "あぁ、今回の夏フェスではライブの他に\nアイドル同士が対決する企画もあるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ in this summer festival‚ there's a plan for idols to compete against each other‚\nin addition to the live performances.",
